     <td class="titlecell" valign="top"><div class="left"><h2>Bodensee-Zugspitze (Edit)</h2></div><div class="right"><a class="textlink" href="posting.php?id=247624&amp;page=0&amp;category=all&amp;order=last_answer&amp;descasc=DESC&amp;view=board" title="auf dieses Posting antworten">antworten</a></div></td>
